# ðŸ§  Resume Analyzer Tool

A smart full-stack application that parses resumes in PDF format, extracts key information, matches user skills to job roles, and provides feedback and matched job suggestions.

## ðŸš€ Features

- Upload and parse PDF resumes
- Extract fields: Name, Email, Phone, Education, Experience, Skills
- Analyze resume quality and generate suggestions
- Match candidate skills to relevant job listings
- Resume dashboard with deletion and detail views
- Toast alerts and confirmation modals
- MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js stack

## ðŸ›  Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, Tailwind CSS, Axios, React-Hot-Toast
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express, Multer, pdf-parse
- **Database:** MongoDB + Mongoose
